metadata.name: Glyph #1
metadata.description:
Title: Glyph #1

Artist: Brian Bixby

Medium: Digital Photograph

Original Dimensions: 51.34 x 76.91 cm

Edition: 1/1

Additional Information: Glyph is an NFT photography collection from Brian Bixby, a series of 1/1 photographs that document ephemeral sculptures built from recycled cardboard boxes. After being photographed the materials are recycled again and all that remains are the photographs. 

Photograph made in Weimar, Germany, October 2018.
